text: Miroslav Málek (30 November 1915 – 30 November 1995) was a Czech gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1915 births Category:1995 deaths Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Prague
